  "detailed_description": "Anatidae is a precision platform game about a little duck with amazing skills. Your objective is catch the max golden eggs that you can! Do you have what it takes to go through all the challenges?<br><br>In Anatidae, you'll need to think fast and use your disponible skills to pass the obstacles. Find secret passages and be quick to escape from death. You'll no longer trust walls after playing!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618450/extras/6054cd5bed9ab41d28ea6a5c62796d4a.poster.avif?t=1704634833\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618450/extras/6054cd5bed9ab41d28ea6a5c62796d4a.webm?t=1704634833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50+ levels: Over fifty challenging and trapped levels!<br></li><li>20+ skins: Over twenty skins, with variations, for you to display through the levels!<br></li><li>10+ mechanics: Over ten different mechanics that combined form great challenges!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618450/extras/07920778b6553907794dfbb53691a6bc.poster.avif?t=1704634833\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618450/extras/07920778b6553907794dfbb53691a6bc.webm?t=1704634833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
